text: Nina Kunzendorf Nina Kunzendorf (born November 10, 1971) is a German actress. Her credits include the television series Tatort and the films Phoenix, Woman in Gold and Unspoken. Kunzendorf was born in Mannheim, Baden-Württemberg. ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:German film actresses Category:German television actresses Category:21st-century German actresses Category:1971 births Category:People from Mannheim
